== icon appears at bottom of page? ==

Hi, I just realized that the status icon is not visible when logged in, and it appears at the bottom of a page instead of at the top right when not logged in (see for example [[Spanish by Choice]]). I think I liked the previous layout better. --[[User:Martin Kraus|Martin Kraus]] ([[User talk:Martin Kraus|discuss]] • [[Special:Contributions/Martin Kraus|contribs]])

