To display a shortcut or shortcuts, simply include the shortcuts as unnamed parameters.
:{{tlx|obsolete|WB:CHAT}}
{{obsolete|WB:CHAT}}

Both a shortcut and superseding page can be included.
:{{tlx|obsolete|WB:CHAT|superseded{{=}}Wikibooks:Reading room}}
{{obsolete|WB:CHAT|superseded=Wikibooks:Reading room}}

