{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES AND INTERWIKIS AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE -->
This template shows the last time a page was edited in days, weeks or months with default being days.
=== Usage ===
{{tlx|lastedit}} produces {{lastedit}}

{{tlx|lastedit|days}} produces {{lastedit|days}}

{{tlx|lastedit|weeks}} produces {{lastedit|weeks}}

{{tlx|lastedit|months}} produces {{lastedit|months}}

=== See also ===
*{{tl|time ago}} &ndash; similar, but includes "''units'' ago" following output
